    SC -->|"PVC provisioning"| WORKERS
    SC -->|"PVC provisioning"| INFRA

    OAUTH --- LDAP_IDP
    CERTOP --- CERTS
    ARGO --- TEKTON
    SMCP --- KIALI
    OVN --- MULTUS --- SRIOV

    WORKERS -->|"mTLS sidecar"| SMCP
    WORKERS -->|"multi-NIC"| MULTUS
